state.description:
Possible values for *state*:
- *off* - the mapped address space is disabled or the module is disabled;
- *failed* - the mapped address space failed to come up (so, it is unavailable, athough it is enabled);
- *good* - the mapped address space is up and with no issues;
- *warning* - the mapped address space is up, but there were warnings;
- *loading* - address space loading is in progress.
- *missing* - address space cannot be loaded because one or more missing dependencies
